{"title":"煤海浪花","authors":["禾波"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":3,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤海浪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇妙的井口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这奇妙的井口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难分夜晚白昼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯光像灿烂的宝石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把深邃的矿井照透。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绞车粗大的钢绳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧拉着成串的煤斗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个下井的空罐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上来时都把煤堆成山丘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地下富饶的煤矿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知有多宽多厚？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长年累月采掘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找不到它的尽头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百个地下尖兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来去都经过井口；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每次夺煤大战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是胜利、丰收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么奇妙的井口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎会有涌不完的煤流？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像矿工的炽热的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远不歇的熊熊烈火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汹涌澎湃的煤流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像山洪一样怒吼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从煤墙狂奔直下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷带着岩石飞走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这珍贵如金的墨玉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜不停地奔流；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蕴藏在地壳底层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出自矿工的巨手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英勇无畏的矿工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮志充满宇宙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用无比锋利的水枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在地下忘我搏斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎顽石的阻挡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斩断煤层的咽喉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以移山填海的气概，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把地下的乌龙押走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔滔不断的煤流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌出神奇的井口；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在每个煤罐中间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有矿工给祖国的问候。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地下满眼星星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星星分外光明；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一片灿烂的星海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮幽深的矿井。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽敞的巷道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狭窄的石门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有那低矮的曲径，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都变作美丽的仙境。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井下和暖如春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风锤电钻声声；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士在星光底下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛夺大量乌金。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的井下电工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是创造幸福的奇人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用一双长着厚茧的大手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给矿井摘来满天繁星。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}